{{!--
  Icon font stylesheet — Material Symbols (Outlined).

  Default loads from Google Fonts CDN. For privacy-conscious,
  air-gapped, or GDPR-sensitive deployments, override at
  <config_dir>/templates/partials/icon-font.hbs to:

    - Self-host: vendor the font and load via /static/.
    - Skip entirely: leave the file empty (icons render as raw
      glyph names; the admin remains functional).
    - Swap families: replace with a different icon font.

  Used by both `<crap-*>` components and `.material-symbols-outlined`
  spans throughout the templates. Icon size + colour are CSS
  utilities (`.icon--sm`, `.icon--muted`) defined in
  `styles/base/reset.css`.
--}}
